xt\ a_{i+1} = a_i\) . By construction \(a_1 \in P(a_i)\) . In case we terminated, we have found a leave node that contains \(a_1\) as a parent. In case we never terminated, we get an infiite sequence \(a_i \in N\) , hence \(a_i = a_j\) for some \(i<j\) . And we found a cycle. Contradiction. Maybe singles would have been a better name, but we stick to the more traditional terminology established for trees here. ↩

